Corey Hertz is a highly accomplished Chief Product Officer and technologist with a wealth of experience in developing innovative products and solutions for technology companies. With a career spanning more than 15 years, Corey has honed his skills in product management, software engineering, and strategic planning.


Throughout his career, Corey has worked with a diverse range of companies, from early-stage startups to Fortune 500 enterprises. He has played a key role in developing and launching successful products in a variety of industries, including SaaS, mobile, and e-commerce.


Corey is known for his ability to translate complex technical concepts into business solutions that drive growth and innovation. He has a deep understanding of emerging technologies, and is skilled at identifying and capitalizing on market opportunities.
